msgid "Why does Mozilla restrict deleted add-ons?"
msgstr "Cogodla Mozilla wulašowane dodanki wobgranicujo?"

#: src/amo/pages/Block/index.js:245
msgid ""
"When the author deletes their add-on, it's no longer maintained or updated, "
"which could compromise Firefox security, stability, or performance. To "
"prevent this, the add-on will be restricted from general use to protect "
"Firefox users. For more information, please read %(supportStartLink)sthis "
"support article%(supportEndLink)s."
msgstr ""
"Gaž awtor swój dodank lašujo, njebuźo se wěcej wótwardowaś abo "
"aktualizěrowaś, což móžo wěstotu, stabilnosć abo wugbaśe Firefox pómjeńšyś. "
"Aby se togo wobinuło, se powšykne wužywanje dodanka wobgranicujo, aby "
"wužywarjow šćitali. Za dalšne informacije cytajśo pšosym "
"%(supportStartLink)stoś ten nastawk pomocy%(supportEndLink)s."

#: src/amo/pages/Block/index.js:263
msgid "How does Mozilla enforce its policies?"
msgstr "Kak Mozilla swóje pšawidła pśesajźujo?"

#: src/amo/pages/Block/index.js:269
msgid ""
"When Mozilla becomes aware of add-ons, plugins, or other third-party "
"software that seriously compromise Firefox security, stability, or "
"performance and meet %(criteriaStartLink)scertain "
"criteria%(criteriaEndLink)s, the software may be blocked or restricted from "
"general use. For more information, please read %(supportStartLink)sthis "
"support article%(supportEndLink)s."
