msgstr "Instalaija jo se pśetergnuła, dokulaž dodank zda se wobškóźony byś."

#: src/amo/utils/addons.js:39
msgid "Installation failed. Please try again."
msgstr "Instalacija njejo se raźiła. Pšosym wopytajśo hyšći raz."

#: src/amo/utils/addons.js:41
msgid "Download failed. Please check your connection."
msgstr "Ześěgnjenje njejo se raźiło. Pšosym pśeglědujśo swój zwisk."

#: src/amo/utils/addons.js:43
msgid "An unexpected error occurred during installation."
msgstr "Pśi instalěrowanje jo njewótcakana zmólka nastała."

#: src/amo/utils/addons.js:45
msgid "An unexpected error occurred during uninstallation."
msgstr "Pśi wótinstalěrowanju jo njewótcakana zmólka nastała."

#: src/amo/utils/addons.js:50
msgid "An unexpected error occurred."
msgstr "Njewótcakana zmólka jo nastała."

#: src/amo/utils/notifications.js:10
msgid ""
"stay up-to-date with news and events relevant to add-on developers "
"(including the about:addons newsletter)"
msgstr ""
"wostańśo aktualny z powěsćami a tšojenjami, kótarež su relewantne za "
"wuwijarje (inkluziwnje powěsćowy list about:addons)"

#: src/amo/utils/notifications.js:13
msgid "Mozilla needs to contact me about my individual add-on"
msgstr "Mozilla musy se ze mnu mójogo dodanka dla do zwiska stajiś"

#: src/amo/utils/notifications.js:16
msgid "new add-ons or Firefox features are available"
msgstr "nowe dodanki abo funkcije Firefox su k dispoziciji"

#: src/amo/utils/notifications.js:18
msgid "someone writes a review of my add-on"
msgstr "něchten pišo pógódnośenje mójogo dodanka"

#: src/amo/utils/notifications.js:20
msgid "an add-on developer replies to my review"
msgstr "wuwijaŕ dodanka wótegranja na mójo pógódnośenje"

#: src/amo/utils/notifications.js:22
msgid "my add-on is reviewed by a reviewer"
msgstr "mój dodank jo se wót redaktora pśeglědał"

#: src/amo/utils/notifications.js:24
msgid "my add-on's compatibility cannot be upgraded"
msgstr "kompatibelnosć mójogo dodanka njedajo se pówušyś"

#: src/amo/utils/notifications.js:26
msgid "my add-on's compatibility is upgraded successfully"
msgstr "Kompatibelnosć mójogo dodanka jo se wuspěšnje pówušiła"

#: src/amo/utils/promoted.js:40
msgid ""
"Official add-on built by Mozilla Firefox. Meets security and performance "
"standards."
msgstr ""
"Oficielny dodank, wuwity za Mozilla Firefox. Docynja wěstotne a wugbaśowe "
"standardy."

#: src/amo/utils/promoted.js:50
msgid ""
"Firefox only recommends add-ons that meet our standards for security and "
"performance."
msgstr ""
"Firefox jano dodanki dopórucujo, kótarež našym standardam za wěstotu a "
"wugbaśe wótpowěduju."
